In [2]:
x = np.linspace(0,10,100)
y = np.sin(x)
z = np.cos(x)
In [3]:
def plot(sty):
    print("Use style: %s" %sty)
    plt.style.use(sty)
    plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
    plt.plot(x,y,'.-',label=r"sin$\alpha$")
    plt.plot(x,z,'o--',label=r"cosin$\alpha$")
    plt.xlabel(r"$\alpha$ [rad]")
    plt.ylabel(r"Value $R_{MTJ}$")
    plt.title("style=%s" %sty)
    plt.legend()
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()
    plt.close()
